PN,37201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FA forensic psychiatrist who
OL,8,Frecommended that triple killer Valdo
OL,9,FCalocane be given a hospital order,
OL,10,Fdid not view footage of previous
OL,11,Fincidents he had been involved in
OL,12,Fbefore writing his report, the
OL,13,FNottingham attacks inquiry has heard.
OL,15,FParanoid schizophrenic Calocane was
OL,16,Fsentenced to an indefinite hospital
OL,17,Forder in January 2024 after admitting
OL,18,Fthree counts of manslaughter by
OL,19,Fdiminished responsibility.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FHe fatally stabbed students Barnaby
OL,8,FWebber and Grace O'Malley-Kumar, 19,
OL,9,Fas well as school caretaker Ian
OL,10,FCoates, 65, and three counts of
OL,11,Fattempted murder during a violent
OL,12,Frampage in Nottingham in June 2023.
OL,14,FThree psychiatrists, including
OL,15,FProfessor Nigel Blackwood, recommended
OL,16,Fin reports written ahead of Calocane's
OL,17,Fsentencing hearing at Nottingham Crown
OL,18,FCourt that a hospital order with
OL,19,Frestrictions was the most appropriate
OL,20,Fsentence based on his mental illness.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FGiving evidence at the central London
OL,8,Finquiry on Monday, Prof Blackwood,
OL,9,Fwhose opinion was that Calocane's
OL,10,Fresponsibility for the offences was at
OL,11,Fthe "lower end of the spectrum", said
OL,12,Fhe did not see body-worn video footage
OL,13,For hear audio of key moments in the
OL,14,Fyears before the fatal attacks.
OL,26,@sD@EOUsD@_O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FHe said Calocane was a "complicated
OL,8,Fman to assess" and that he was not
OL,9,Fsent body-worn video of when the
OL,10,Fmechanical engineering graduate
OL,11,Fvisited the MI5 headquarters in London
OL,12,Fin May 2021, audio of a 999 call a
OL,13,Fhousemate had made after Calocane
OL,14,Fassaulted him in July 2021, or footage
OL,15,Fof an assault on a police officer in
OL,16,FSeptember 2021.
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@NO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FProf Blackwood said the MI5 video only
OL,8,Femerged after his report in November
OL,9,F2023 was written, telling the inquiry:
OL,10,F"I was aware of it at the time of the
OL,11,Fsentencing... confirming his
OL,12,Fdelusional belief about interference
OL,13,Fabout MI5 and wanting them to desist."
OL,15,FHe said he had received a witness
OL,16,Fstatement from the student, named only
OL,17,Fas Sebastian, who had been grabbed by
OL,18,FCalocane, but did not recall listening
OL,19,Fto the 999 call he had made.
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FOf the attack on Pc Barnaby Pritchard,
OL,8,Fwho had been called to assist when
OL,9,FCalocane was refusing to be detained
OL,10,Fby doctors under mental health laws,
OL,11,Fcounsel to the inquiry Rachel Langdale
OL,12,FKC said: "That's really important
OL,13,Ffootage isn't it?
OL,15,F"You assessed VC's version ` he told
OL,16,Fyou he had been highly fearful that
OL,17,Fthe conspiracy was intent on harming
OL,18,Fhim. He considered that intelligence
OL,19,Fagencies and the police were behind
OL,20,Fthe plot.
OL,26,@tD@JOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,F"In this fearful state he headbutted
OL,8,Fthe officer who executed the section
OL,9,F135 warrant.
OL,11,F"That is what he tells you ` but did
OL,12,Fyou have anything to test that account
OL,13,Fby? It sounds like you didn't."
OL,15,F"No, I don't think I did," Prof
OL,16,FBlackwood said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUuD@_O]wD@AOUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FPolice body-worn camera footage of the
OL,8,Fmoment armed police were called after
OL,9,Ftriple killer Valdo Calocane
OL,10,Fapproached the headquarters of MI5 was
OL,11,Fshown at the Nottingham attacks
OL,12,Finquiry on 3 March.
OL,14,FMs Langdale said while Calocane
OL,15,Fdescribed it as a headbutting, the
OL,16,Ffootage actually shows him refusing to
OL,17,Fgo into an ambulance, taking off his
OL,18,Fglasses and placing them aside before
OL,19,Ftelling the only male police officer
OL,20,Fhe wanted him to "take him out",
OL,21,Fsaying: "I don't harm women."
OL,26,@|D@ROU|D@_O]}D@IOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FShe said: "Only one of the officers
OL,8,Fpicks up what he is indicating, that
OL,9,Fhe wants to harm a male officer and
OL,10,Fnot a female officer, and from nought
OL,11,Fto 100 that goes really quickly.
OL,13,F"He selects the male officer. Would
OL,14,Fthat have been helpful for you to see
OL,15,Fhow that unravelled, that he chooses
OL,16,Fwho he is going to assault and he
OL,17,Fassaults them?"
OL,19,FProf Blackwood said: "Yes, I don't
OL,20,Fthink it's countervailing evidence
OL,21,Fthat he's psychotic at that moment."
OL,26,@oD@KOUuD@AOUyD@OO]{D@VOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FHe accepted it "could have been"
OL,8,Fhelpful to have seen that footage.
OL,10,FMs Langdale said: "He is capable of
OL,11,Fassessing, in those circumstances,
OL,12,Fwhatever his psychosis, who he wants
OL,13,Fto attack and why."
OL,15,FFootage of Calocane's assault on
OL,16,Fanother flatmate, named as
OL,17,FChristopher, whom he got in a headlock
OL,18,Fafter he was asked to clean their
OL,19,Fshared bathroom, was also not seen by
OL,20,FProf Blackwood before he made his
OL,21,Fassessment.
OL,26,@oD@POUoD@`O]rD@SOUuD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FAsked if he agreed that the behaviour
OL,8,Fshown by Calocane was "bullying and
OL,9,Fintimidating", Prof Blackwood said:
OL,10,F"He's psychotic at this point, he is
OL,11,Fhearing screams elsewhere in the flat,
OL,12,Fhe has had a conflict with a flatmate
OL,13,Fabout his hygiene but yes, he is
OL,14,Fclearly asserting his physical
OL,15,Fdominance over that flatmate."
OL,26,@pD@WOUqD@MO]rD@AOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FThe inquiry also heard Calocane told
OL,8,FProf Blackwood his difficulties with
OL,9,Fhis mental health had started in 2019,
OL,10,Fbut a statement obtained by the
OL,11,Finquiry team from a woman who shared
OL,12,Faccommodation with Calocane between
OL,13,F2014 and 2015 suggested he was "quiet,
OL,14,Funfriendly, and did not appear to want
OL,15,Fto socialise".
OL,26,@uD@`OUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FShe recalled "unusual behaviour" such
OL,8,Fas being in the kitchen several times
OL,9,Fduring the night, screaming coming
OL,10,Ffrom his room, standing in the garden
OL,11,Fin the dark and raising his voice
OL,12,Fafter being asked about missing food.
OL,14,FProf Blackwood said: "This was not
OL,15,Favailable to me at the time I wrote my
OL,16,Finitial report.
OL,18,F"This would suggest there were pre-
OL,19,Fmorbid features of psychosis earlier
OL,20,Fthan by his own description.
OL,26,@oD@NOUoD@`O]vD@VOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,F"I think this speaks to a longer
OL,8,Ftimeline of his psychotic illness than
OL,9,Fany particular personality features.
OL,11,F"It speaks more to, potentially, a
OL,12,Flonger timeline of the development of
OL,13,Fhis psychotic illness rather than
OL,14,Fseparate personality difficulties."
OL,16,FAnalysis of Calocane's phone also
OL,17,Ffound he had videos of the 2022
OL,18,FBuffalo shooting and the 2019
OL,19,FChristchurch Mosque attacks, as well
OL,20,Fas images of Adolf Hitler, Nazi
OL,21,Fsoldiers and weapons.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUvD@cO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FProf Blackwood said he did not ask
OL,8,FCalocane why he had those on his phone.
OL,10,FHe said: "I interpret those in the
OL,11,Fcontext of his untreated psychosis, he
OL,12,Fis angry, he is perplexed ` 'why are
OL,13,Fmy thoughts being monitored by the
OL,14,Fgovernment or a rogue computer
OL,15,Fprogramme, why am I being tormented by
OL,16,Fthese individuals?' and in the context
OL,17,Fof this he is looking at different
OL,18,Finformation about Hitler, the Nazis,
OL,19,Fshootings etc."
OL,26,@rD@JOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FHe added: "It may be that he is
OL,8,Fsearching for an understanding, he is
OL,9,Flooking at the way in which others
OL,10,Fhave reacted to these things, it may
OL,11,Fbe that he already has murderous
OL,12,Fintentions by this point and that is
OL,13,Fwhy he is looking at such material."
OL,15,FAsked by Ms Langdale if Calocane was a
OL,16,F"dangerous" man, he said: "I think his
OL,17,Frisk to others has increased as a
OL,18,Fresult of his psychotic illness, yes."
OL,26,@oD@KOUuD@dO]xD@AOUxD@KO]xD@[OUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774969867
OL,3,CForensic psychiatrist did not view
OL,4,Cfootage of previous Valdo Calocane
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FProf Blackwood said he did not believe
OL,8,FCalocane had been manipulative in his
OL,9,Fpolice interviews, in which he
OL,10,Fanswered some questions but would not
OL,11,Fanswer others.
OL,13,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G17/17
